                            <comment id="13032420" author="slebresne" created="Thu, 12 May 2011 14:07:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch attach with a unit test. We were considering the mutation from the CL as coming from remote host and thus not considering them as new increment (and thus we were keeping the max instead of summing)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13032434" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 12 May 2011 14:45:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;comment needs update:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;                 // This is coming from a remote host
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;otherwise, +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13032456" author="slebresne" created="Thu, 12 May 2011 15:22:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed with comment removed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13032776" author="hudson" created="Fri, 13 May 2011 00:52:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra-0.8 #103 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra-0.8/103/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra-0.8/103/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
